      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.floridaspringscouncil.org/rainbow"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "During Florida’s 1960s tourism boom, visitors chased waterfalls, animals, and a “jungle oasis”; the park closed in 1973 and the state took over in 1990.",
